Package siminov.orm.reader

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationDescriptorReader
    Exposes methods to parse Application Descriptor information as per define in ApplicationDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
    DatabaseDescriptorReader
    Exposes methods to parse Database Descriptor information as per define in DatabaseDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
    DatabaseMappingDescriptorReader
    Exposes methods to parse Library Descriptor information as per define in DatabaseDescriptor.si.xml or LibraryDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
    LibraryDescriptorReader
    Exposes methods to parse Library Descriptor information as per define in LibraryDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
    QuickDatabaseMappingDescriptorReader
    Exposes methods to quickly parse database mapping descriptor defined by application.
    SiminovSAXDefaultHandler
    Exposes common methods which are required by every SIMINOV parsers.
